'''直布羅陀灣'''（{{lang-es|Bahía de Algeciras}}）是[[西班牙|西班牙]]的海灣，位於[[伊比利亞半島|伊比利亞半島]]南端，長10公里、寬8公里，面積75平方公里，最大水深400米，南面是[[直布羅陀海峽|直布羅陀海峽]]和[[地中海|地中海]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dur.ac.uk/resources/ibru/publications/full/bsb7-1_oreilly.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-07-06 |archive-date=2012-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012005917/http://www.dur.ac.uk/resources/ibru/publications/full/bsb7-1_oreilly.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.firmm.org/en/news/article/items/impressions-of-a-course-participant-part-1 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-07-06 |archive-date=2019-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527090729/https://www.firmm.org/en/news/article/items/impressions-of-a-course-participant-part-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
==歷史==
[[File:Gibraltar_and_Bay_map_1750.jpg|thumb]]]]
直布羅陀灣及臨近的地區已被使用超過3000年了。 隨後，[[摩爾人|摩爾人]]及[[西班牙人|西班牙人]]也在[[中世紀|中世紀]]於此處定居。在1704年，英軍佔領了[[直布羅陀|直布羅陀]]。
現時[[西班牙|西班牙]]正與[[英國|英國]]爭執直布羅陀的管制權。有些西班牙漁民也在非法地在英國直布羅陀海域捕魚<ref>[http://www.hydrographicsociety.org/Articles/journal/2000/95-2.htm Gerry O'Reilly, "Gibraltar: Sovereignty Disputes and Territorial Waters", in ''The Hydrographic Journal'' No 95, January 2000] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060503025537/http://www.hydrographicsociety.org/Articles/journal/2000/95-2.htm |date=2006-05-03 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.un.org/Depts/los/convention_agreements/convention_overview_convention.htm |title=UN Law of the Seas website |accessdate=2014-07-06 |archive-date=2015-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151103052713/http://www.un.org/Depts/los/convention_agreements/convention_overview_convention.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/scienceNews/idUSN2046348920080820 Peru joins in Spanish claim]</ref>。

